author: Nathaniel Sena <nate.sena1@gmail.com>
message:
Add Git Change Intelligence system documentation

- Add comprehensive documentation for Git-based processing system
- Focus on meaningful change analysis rather than file processing
- Include 5-task implementation plan: Git Diff Parser, Commit Message Reader, Change Analyzer, Memory Creator, Simple CLI
- Document workflow from commit to knowledge graph memory
- Include example use cases and technical requirements
- Plan for future enhancements and error handling
